{"type":null,"faqId":13466,"title":"G730-L075 屏幕自动黑屏，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">通话过程中屏幕自动黑屏。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">这是正常现象。是由于手机听筒靠近头部时，听筒附近的接近光传感器被遮挡，屏幕自动关闭，进入省电模式。当手机离开头部，屏幕自动点亮。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">为了保证手机的正常使用，请注意不要用手机套或其他物体遮挡听筒附近的屏幕。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">运行某些不兼容的第三方应用程序时屏幕黑屏。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">请卸载该应用程序或备份重要数据后将手机恢复出厂设置。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">同时运行过多应用程序可能会导致屏幕黑屏。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">彻底关闭后台暂时不需要的应用程序：在<b>设置</b>界面，点击<b>管理应用程序</b>，点击您要关闭的应用程序，然后点击<b>停止</b>，即可关闭此程序。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:106.3pt;\">\n\t<span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=43328\" width=\"501\" height=\"270\" alt=\"\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>* </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span><span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":5,"unUseful":14,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4607","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1404705454000,"seriesProductName":"G730-L075","visitedTimes":1937,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"G730-L075","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}